<br>
2. Comeon... we have been smacked in the noggin OUR WHOLE FREAKING LIFE. Concussions, Brain Hemmorage, cracked skull, brains splattered across rocks, you name any head injury, we've had it. And we still can pretty much talk clearly. So why does one or two beers mess that up! Our brains are way too scrambled already for a freaking shot to do any damage!<br>
<br>
Raise our Alcohol Tolerance. It's balanced Pre-50, but post 50, 225-235 would NOT be out of line!<br>
<br>
3. Not warrior only, but comeon, casters can specialize in spells! DAMMIT! Let taunt-using classes specialize in a language! Warriors would spend all day taunting Kobolds, day in and day out, should be able to hit 252 in Kobold language! Give us a quest to resest specialization, too- Give an emerald to some dude, he smashes your head in with a really large hammer (Would take several blows, see my post about our tough brains) and we forget all we learned, and start out with 49 in every language!<br>
<br>
