<br>
5. Last, but NOT FREAKING LEAST BY A LONG SHOT. Pallies get LoH every 72 min. SK's get HT. Give us something equal, dammit! I want either Bind Sight or Eye of Zomm on my once a day ability! That way when I am stuck in camp and only the puller and all the classes with bind sight and eye of zomm can see anything expect for the room we are camped it, I can see stuff too!<br>
